sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 用户
    participant Core as agentic_rag 主循环
    participant Decide as decide 决策
    participant Tools as TOOLS 工具
    participant VS as 向量库

    User->>Core: question
    Core->>Core: 构造 messages system user

    loop 最多 max_steps=5 步
        Core->>Decide: decide(messages)
        alt 返回 type == final
            Decide-->>Core: text
            Core-->>User: ✅ Final Answer
        else 返回 type == tools
            Decide-->>Core: calls name args id
            Core->>Core: messages.append assistant
            loop 遍历每个 tool call
                Core->>Core: 💭 Thought / ⚡ Action
                Core->>Tools: TOOLS name args
                alt 检索超时 TimeoutError
                    Tools-->>Core: raise TimeoutError
                    Core-->>User: ⏱ 降级 LLM 直答 未经文档验证
                else 正常返回
                    Tools->>VS: 读取 store 并打分排序
                    VS-->>Tools: top_k results
                    Tools-->>Core: 👁 Observation status results
                    Core->>Core: messages.append tool result
                end
            end
        end
    end
